data.description: Fantastic home at The Settlement in Plainfield featuring 4 BR & 2.5 BA. Main floor features large main living space and great flex room for home office or reading room. Kitchen features full suite of stainless steal appliances, a beautiful center island that can be used for dining. Head upstairs to your spacious 18x12 loft area and a nice 20x14 primary suite featuring a glass walk in shower & 2 spacious WIC. Three other bedrooms upstairs too! Attached 2 car garage and nice size backyard! The home also features a Solar power system to keep your electric bills low!
